# Ignore everything by default
*

# --- Keep top-level folders ---
!scripts/
!scripts/**
!jobs/
!jobs/**

# --- Keep simulations subfolders ---
!simulations/
!simulations/jobs/
!simulations/jobs/**
# simulations/analysis/ is excluded (generated output)
!simulations/scripts/
!simulations/scripts/**
!simulations/networks/
!simulations/networks/**
!simulations/md_files/
!simulations/md_files/**
!simulations/*.md
!simulations/summary_config.yaml

# --- Keep ml_method folder ---
!ml_method/
!ml_method/**

# --- Always keep key files ---
!.gitignore
!README.md
!CLAUDE.md
